dct_description_sm: Engraved map of France showing towns, roads and provinces with relief shown pictorially. "This new map is laid down according to the observations and actuall surveys, lately made by the Royall Academy of France. H. Moll fecit." Page 57 from section titled France in: A system of geography : or, A new and accurate description of the earth, in all its empires, kingdoms and states. Illustrated with history and topography, and maps of every country ... / by Herman Moll. London : Printed for Tim Childe ..., 1701.
